{"tid":2106204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊內部分歧 斥協議賣國","createTime":"2020-07-13T07:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T08:19:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6d08bba47b7177d7dce4ac2a83656fdde621e3ee","tid":2106204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200713/GXV7QB5DQPFI6EKNHVJYDMFW7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200713%2FGXV7QB5DQPFI6EKNHVJYDMFW7U%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxHKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=6154c5d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200713%2FGXV7QB5DQPFI6EKNHVJYDMFW7U%2F&h=d67741d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200713/GXV7QB5DQPFI6EKNHVJYDMFW7U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n伊內部分歧 斥協議賣國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EehshBchV6nDuIkBOrxU8NEb-mQ=/1026x684/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R2DT4M6DXBR462Q6BE2FMJA6S4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEehshBchV6nDuIkBOrxU8NEb-mQ%3D%2F1026x684%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR2DT4M6DXBR462Q6BE2FMJA6S4.gif&h=ede44749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國是伊朗原油最大買家，圖為運油輪將伊朗原油運至浙江省舟山市。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n中伊協議仍未正式公開，但已在伊朗內部引起爭議，外長扎里夫上周在國會被議員嚴詞質詢，稱協議「沒甚麼秘密」，協議內容敲定後會提交國會作最後審批。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗最高精神領袖哈梅內伊和總統魯哈尼內閣，據報都支持協議。哈梅內伊的首席經濟顧問穆罕默迪，近日在國營電視台指，伊朗有需要將原油產量提高至每日至少850萬桶，否則會在能源市場失去影響地位，所以需要中國。<br />\n<br />\n支持協議人士指伊朗在經濟合作上的選擇少、貨幣正插水式急跌，又難。<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n國的路開通。在撤銷制裁之前，這協議無論怎樣都是最佳選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國投資累多國債台高築<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《紐時》揭華25年投資3萬億  中國伊朗密議曝光 近百基建換石油<br />\n<br />\n但來自伊朗不同政治光譜的批評者，質疑政府在經濟疲弱和在國際被<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n容這是可疑的秘密協議，伊朗人民永遠不會同意。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"ff82270512ae39e66605be80edcc0d24f794c8bc","tid":2106204,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:54:04.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d76250f4a4b81e07a736a55067fc7b29bf56c13","tid":2106204,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"99a4ab3c2d9f5bc0c18d79f90cd42649b0946a62","tid":2106204,"uid":52962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"最大嘅問題係買賣係用人民幣結算<br />\n伊朗坐咁多人民幣係咪諗住全國人民搬去中國洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cc7def43d5db2be32c844f35e8b693d7c7d5f0","tid":2106204,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99a4ab3c2d9f5bc0c18d79f90cd42649b0946a62","tid":2106204,"uid":52962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"最大嘅問題係買賣係用人民幣結算<br />\n伊朗坐咁多人民幣係咪諗住全國人民搬去中國洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:04:08.000Z","msg":"是旦印D 爛9 鬼國幣<br />\n同你換石油 FATFAT"},{"pid":"d8a3911c4eac74870a39dd79fae0e68320fbdb81","tid":2106204,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"仲以中國係好朋友？只係趁你病就拎盡你著數咋.."},{"pid":"d7eebf4450e4809775d762698a848e7a826cec3d","tid":2106204,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"信唔信丫，最後都係照奶<br />\n美帝殺左蘇萊曼尼=敵人<br />\n美帝敵人=支共<br />\n敵人嘅敵人=朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba926270b856f8b2bd2d87ff5035c2b0aad2d46f","tid":2106204,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"習近平：中國是和平可親文明獅子<img src=\"